      <h2 class="c-section__title vh">Pacific Waves: News&nbsp;In&nbsp;Depth</h2>
    <div class="c-top-stories__primary primary layout--standard has-secondary item-count--6">
          <ul class="c-top-stories__list">
                <li class="o-digest o-digest--news o-digest--extended u-blocklink has-thumbnail">
<div class="thumb-container" aria-hidden="true">
<img class="four_col " loading="lazy" alt="Solomon Islands Prime Minister Manasseh Sogavare" width="576" height="288" src="https://media.rnztools.nz/rnz/image/upload/s--uBzG_Phi--/ar_16:10,c_fill,f_auto,g_auto,q_auto,w_576/v1689648327/4L5O8CA_Solomon_Islands_Prime_Minister_Manasseh_Sogavare_1140x570_webp" />
</div>
<div class="o-digest__detail">
<h3 class="o-digest__headline" lang=""><a class="faux-link" href="/international/pacific-news/515368/solomon-islands-opposition-parties-combine-in-race-to-form-government">Solomon Islands opposition parties combine in race to form government</a></h3>
<div class="o-kicker">
<div class="o-kicker__zones">
<span class="kicker-item"><a href="/international/pacific-news">Pacific</a></span>
</div>

<span class="o-kicker__time kicker-item"></span>
</div>
<div class="o-digest__summary">
<p lang="">The two main opposition parties are vying with the former prime minister's party to form a government, after an election delivered no clear winner.</p>
</div>
</div>
<a aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" class="u-blocklink__overlay-link" href="/international/pacific-news/515368/solomon-islands-opposition-parties-combine-in-race-to-form-government">Solomon Islands opposition parties combine in race to form government</a>
</li>

                <li class="o-digest o-digest--news o-digest--extended u-blocklink has-thumbnail">
<div class="thumb-container" aria-hidden="true">
