</div>
<div class="o-digest__detail">
<h3 class="o-digest__headline" lang=""><a class="faux-link" href="/international/pacific-news/515348/removal-of-kiribati-high-court-judge-david-lambourne-a-major-setback-for-justice-un">UN &#39;very concerned&#39; about Kiribati Parliament&#39;s move to deport judge</a></h3>
<div class="o-kicker">
<div class="o-kicker__zones">
<span class="kicker-item"><a href="/international/pacific-news">Pacific</a></span>
</div>

<span class="o-kicker__time kicker-item"></span>
</div>
<div class="o-digest__summary">
