</div>
<div class="o-digest__detail">
<h3 class="o-digest__headline" lang=""><a class="faux-link" href="/international/pacific-news/515303/to-lead-is-to-serve-governor-general-to-call-prime-ministerial-election-in-solomon-islands">&quot;To lead is to serve&quot; - Governor General to call prime ministerial election in Solomon Islands</a></h3>
<div class="o-kicker">
<div class="o-kicker__zones">
<span class="kicker-item"><a href="/international/pacific-news">Pacific</a></span>
<span class="kicker-item"><a href="/tags/Solomon%20Islands">Solomon Islands</a></span>
</div>

<span class="o-kicker__time kicker-item"></span>
